        "title": "proflibsって何？",
        "excerpt":"proflibsが何だか分からなかったんだが。 http://lists.freebsd.org/pipermail/freebsd-questions/2008-October/184180.html Re: proflibs by Jeremy Chadwick on 2008-10-11T02:10:33+00:00 On Fri, Oct 10, 2008 at 11:06:11PM -0400, Ansar Mohammed wrote: &#62; Can anyone explain what are the proflibs on the install media, and what they &#62; are for? They're special versions of all the libraries that come with FreeBSD which...","categories": ["FreeBSD"],
